        <item>
          <title>Kris Jenkins, the Villanova hero in 2016 national title game, sues NCAA for money he could have made</title>
          <description><![CDATA[Kris Jenkins, who made the winning shot for Villanova in the 2016 college basketball championship game, is suing the NCAA and six conferences to recoup income he contends he would have earned if athletes at the time were not barred from making money from their name, image and likeness.]]></description>
